{"tid":760811,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曝皇馬1億報價車路士雙星 巴塞沒買到皇馬要買","createTime":"2018-07-30T01:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T09:08:49.000Z","uid":147522,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3426cb38a8bb5355b63501e47c3e0ec06c28b0","tid":760811,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"　　據英國媒體《每日郵報》的消息，皇馬已經向車路士報價1億英鎊，求購車路士隊內兩大球星高圖爾斯加威廉。而車路士方面，正在嚴重考慮這份報價。<br />\n　　關於高圖爾斯，他希望加盟皇馬已經不是秘密，他跟車路士的合約還剩一年。該報指出，高圖爾斯這個夏天一直都是皇馬的目標，皇馬也在等待車路士敲定新門將。藍軍鎖定了史篤城的門將畢特蘭德以及愛華頓門將比基科迪。<br />\n<br />\n　　至於威廉，他一度接近加盟巴塞，但是車路士為他標價7000萬英鎊，最終巴塞選擇放棄，低價選擇了巴西球員馬高姆。皇馬成了威廉的最新買家，銀河戰艦預計威廉轉會費為6500萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n黑世三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d6fec1c9295707921aeef6db57f6f3fc4fb824","tid":760811,"uid":44678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"安仔真世三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29b8d8bbc32024be9a55d2befc4c1d7e4568481","tid":760811,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 幾間豪門爭安世三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d011c0faa4f0d81ea6025ca2b7e9b92b9cc886d5","tid":760811,"uid":60506,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:34:11.000Z","msg":"拿華斯真係慘 連condom都不如 喊晒口都無得留低"},{"pid":"e4f66dfca1ef6ea9821fbcfd26b545b6c0053bc5","tid":760811,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e29b8d8bbc32024be9a55d2befc4c1d7e4568481","tid":760811,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 幾間豪門爭安世三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"車唔放係岩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g